{"tid":1687500,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"財困90後男子　順天邨車內燒炭亡","createTime":"2019-11-02T01:33:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-02T03:42:04.000Z","uid":160807,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"4f8dc29de0ac3318b67c072b599365f196af3ad4","tid":1687500,"uid":160807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T01:33:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191102/photo/bkn-20191102005840760-1102_00822_001_01p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20191102%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20191102005840760-1102_00822_001_01p.jpg&h=d68b8ca2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n昨日(1日)晚上10時13分，警方接獲途人報案，指一名男子在秀茂坪順天邨停車場一輛私家車內暈倒。救護員到場將21歲姓林事主送院搶救，惜最終證實死亡。<br />\n警員於車內發現一盆燒過的炭，但無檢獲遺書，經初步調查將案列自殺，事件無可疑，死因有待剖屍確定。據了解，有人生前曾透露因財政問題感不快。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191102/bkn-20191102005840760-1102_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20191102%2Fbkn-20191102005840760-1102_00822_001.html&d=rxvDypeE%2FV4%2FTsysNGkz8Cq0XD4M5CHb8byFtBYuAsM%3D&h=6fcfb7de\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191102/bkn-20191102005840760-1102_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"a8515842beeb6581d21dcdd7702b24b62eba2430","tid":1687500,"uid":120906,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T01:36:37.000Z","msg":"如果死前殺返一兩隻狗，投胎都投好d，rip"},{"pid":"4dc15401dfe5c1fdea303a0dce18da503eda14e9","tid":1687500,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T01:37:48.000Z","msg":"冇可疑<br />\n依家d狗真係易做"},{"pid":"242db7e1d4ba9a8df22e66f15548782b9431c8df","tid":1687500,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T01:39:46.000Z","msg":"21歲 如果單純因為錢咪破產保護"},{"pid":"437326e3a37687defa6346b40f48f0745ce8eac7","tid":1687500,"uid":279356,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T01:51:04.000Z","msg":"<